        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜AI燒錢成主題 存儲芯片受惠 恒指料守25000點｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/4eb665fd6f44e0af2b8ba088b30ecc4e1afd8d68581850290bfd7abb34e7859a/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fbossmind_356%2F6b0d7f400e3cca9e918861db697902ac\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.谷歌的業績引起了人工智能板塊的分化，下游科網股預計燒錢規模擴大，昨日不單谷歌，微軟、亞馬遜等股價亦明顯下跌至於受惠燒錢的存儲股、芯片股股價則表現硬淨。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.有關的走勢或許同樣影響香港市場，之前反彈的騰訊及阿里巴巴，燒錢同樣有機會引起市場擔心，近期股價開始轉弱。不過，考慮到中國AI成本效益相對較高，受影響或不及美國同業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 如昨日所言，存儲及芯片股暫時是較佳的選擇，此外油價維持高企，相關的石油股、油服股股價預計相對強勢，但畢竟特朗普的政策容易反覆，不如先等油價升至過百後反手做淡油價受惠股。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b8ec2e1e-ee13-32ca-b56b-165145412ef7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4.恒生指數短期阻力在25200點，支持維持看24800點及24500點，超短期支持為25000點，預計在該位將反覆上落。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，熊證街貨再高於牛證，今日若低開可考慮低吸博挾淡。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-ai%E7%87%92%E9%8C%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C-%E5%AD%98%E5%84%B2%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E6%96%99%E5%AE%8825000%E9%BB%9E-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000783.html",
